        <abstract> 
<p>The publishers [of <hi rend="italic">Zoology</hi>] have agreed to 50 plates [for <hi rend="italic">Birds</hi>]. Asks JG to decide which are most worthy of being done. Also asks him to see whether Bayfield will undertake [to colour] the birds (and quadrupeds) at something under 5d each.</p> 
        </abstract>
